# Testing Conventions

## Backend (Python)

- Framework: pytest, async tests via `asyncio_mode = "auto"`
- Location: `tests/` directory per service
- Naming: `test_<behavior>.py`, functions `test_<scenario>`
- Coverage target: 80% statements

## Frontend Unit

- Framework: Vitest (configured in `frontend/vite.config.ts`)
- Environment: jsdom, globals enabled
- Setup: `frontend/src/test/setup.ts`
- Naming: `*.test.tsx`, `*.test.ts`
- Coverage thresholds: 70% statements/lines, 60% branches/functions

## E2E

- Framework: Playwright
- Config: `frontend/playwright.config.ts`
- Location: `frontend/e2e/`
- Browser: Chromium
- Base URL: `http://localhost:5173`
- Naming: `*.spec.ts`
